
 Hotkeys:

   Menu:
   		Open			-	'F1' or 'ESC'
   		Close			-	'F1' or 'ESC'
		Navigation		-	arrows

   List of databases/namespaces/tables:
		Navigation		-	arrows
		Choice			-	'Enter'

   Table data:
		Navigation		-	arrows
		Edit record		-	'e'
		Append record	-	'a' or 'i'
		Delete record	-	'd'
		Close			-	'x'

   Record editing:
		Next column 	-	'Tab' or 'Ctrl+N'
		Previous column	-	'Ctrl+P'
		Confirmation	-	'Enter'
